text: Chris Hunnable (born 19 March 1964) is a British equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:British male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Great Britain Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Braintree, Essex
